<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>4MyIPTV Service Admin Message Templates</title>
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#08111f;
  --panel:#101827;
  --panel-soft:#0b1220;
  --text:#f8fafc;
  --muted:#94a3b8;
  --border:#1f2937;
  --line:#243044;
  --green:#22c55e;
  --blue:#3b82f6;
  --gold:#f59e0b;
  --admin-btn:#1d4ed8;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
body{
  margin:0;
  font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,#08111f,#0f172a);
  color:var(--text);
}
.wrap{max-width:1240px;margin:auto;padding:20px}
.card{
  background:var(--panel);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:18px;
  padding:22px;
  margin-bottom:20px;
  box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
}
h1{margin:0 0 10px;color:#86efac;text-align:center}
h2{margin:0 0 8px;font-size:24px}
h3{margin:0 0 10px;font-size:18px;color:#86efac}
p{margin:0}
.tagline{
  text-align:center;
  margin-bottom:8px;
  color:#cbd5f5;
  font-weight:600;
}
.intro{
  text-align:center;
  color:var(--muted);
  max-width:920px;
  margin:0 auto;
  line-height:1.55;
}
.section-sub{
  color:var(--muted);
  line-height:1.5;
  margin-bottom:16px;
  font-size:14px;
}
.grid-2,.grid-3{
  display:grid;
  gap:16px;
}
.grid-2{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr))}
.grid-3{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr))}
@media (max-width:980px){
  .grid-2,.grid-3{grid-template-columns:1fr}
}
.pill-row,.action-row{
  display:flex;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  gap:10px;
}
.anchor-pill,.action-btn{
  text-decoration:none;
  border-radius:999px;
  font-weight:bold;
}
.anchor-pill{
  display:inline-block;
  padding:8px 12px;
  background:#1e293b;
  color:#fff;
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  font-size:12px;
}
.action-btn{
  display:inline-block;
  padding:11px 14px;
  background:var(--admin-btn);
  color:#fff;
  font-size:14px;
}
.template-box,.info-box{
  background:var(--panel-soft);
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:16px;
  padding:18px;
  height:100%;
}
.template-box p,.info-box p,.template-box li,.info-box li{
  color:#cbd5e1;
  line-height:1.55;
  font-size:14px;
}
.template-copy{
  margin-top:12px;
  padding:14px;
  border-radius:14px;
  background:#0f172a;
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  color:#e2e8f0;
  white-space:pre-line;
  line-height:1.55;
  font-size:14px;
}
.note{
  margin-top:14px;
  padding:12px 14px;
  border-radius:12px;
  background:rgba(59,130,246,.10);
  border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.24);
  color:#dbeafe;
  line-height:1.5;
}
.footer-strip{
  margin-top:18px;
  padding:16px 10px;
  border-top:1px solid #243044;
  text-align:center;
  color:#cbd5e1;
  font-size:.9rem;
}
.footer-strip .version{
  margin-top:6px;
  color:#94a3b8;
  font-size:.82rem;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <div class="card">
    <h1>Admin Message Templates</h1>
    <div class="tagline">4MyIPTV Service Internal Use</div>
    <div class="intro">
      Use this page as the standardized quote-to-payment message reference for customer communication.
      Keep the flow clean: quote, approval, payment, confirmation, fulfillment, and support.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Quick Jump</h2>
    <div class="section-sub">
      Use these anchors to move quickly to the message you need without rewriting the process each time.
    </div>
    <div class="pill-row">
      <a href="#quote-template" class="anchor-pill">Quote</a>
      <a href="#approval-clarification" class="anchor-pill">Approval Clarification</a>
      <a href="#payment-instructions" class="anchor-pill">Payment Instructions</a>
      <a href="#payment-received" class="anchor-pill">Payment Received</a>
      <a href="#service-only" class="anchor-pill">Service Only</a>
      <a href="#device-prep" class="anchor-pill">Device Prep</a>
      <a href="#shipping-confirmation" class="anchor-pill">Shipping</a>
      <a href="#pickup-delivery" class="anchor-pill">Pickup or Delivery</a>
      <a href="#support-handoff" class="anchor-pill">Support Handoff</a>
      <a href="#renewal-quote" class="anchor-pill">Renewal Quote</a>
      <a href="#renewal-payment" class="anchor-pill">Renewal Payment</a>
      <a href="#renewal-complete" class="anchor-pill">Renewal Complete</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Standard Operating Rules</h2>
    <div class="section-sub">
      These are the control rules that keep the message flow clean and consistent.
    </div>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>Approval Rule</h3>
        <p>Always request an explicit approval reply before sending payment instructions. Preferred approval word: Approved.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>Pricing Rule</h3>
        <p>Always show service term, device if applicable, shipping if applicable, and the total amount in the quote and payment messages.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>Sequence Rule</h3>
        <p>Do not overload one message. Keep the sequence as quote, approval, payment, payment received, fulfillment, and support.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="note">
      Best practice: keep service-only orders and device orders clearly separated in the message path so the customer always knows what happens next.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card template-box" id="quote-template">
      <h2>Quote Template</h2>
      <div class="template-copy">Hi [Customer Name],

Thank you for your request. I reviewed your information and prepared your quote below.

Service term: [Monthly / 6 Months / 1 Year / 2 Years]
Service price: [$X]

Device: [None / Device Name]
Device price: [$X]

Shipping: [$X / Not Applicable]

Total: [$X]

What is included:
- [Service term]
- [Device, if applicable]
- [Setup preparation, if applicable]
- [Other included item, if applicable]

If this looks good, please reply:

Approved

Once approved, I will send your payment instructions and next steps.

Thank you,
Timothy
4MyIPTV Service</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card template-box" id="approval-clarification">
      <h2>Approval Clarification</h2>
      <div class="template-copy">Hi [Customer Name],

Thank you. To keep your order moving correctly, please reply with:

Approved

Once I receive that, I will send your payment instructions and next steps.

Thank you,
Timothy
4MyIPTV Service</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card template-box" id="payment-instructions">
      <h2>Payment Instructions</h2>
      <div class="template-copy">Hi [Customer Name],

Thank you. Your order has been approved and is ready for payment.

Order summary:
- Service term: [X]
- Device: [X / None]
- Shipping: [X / Not Applicable]
- Total due: [$X]

Payment link:
[Insert payment link]

After payment is completed, I will follow up with your next steps for [service activation / device preparation / shipping / setup support].

Please reply here after payment is submitted so I can confirm receipt quickly.

Thank you,
Timothy
4MyIPTV Service</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card template-box" id="payment-received">
      <h2>Payment Received</h2>
      <div class="template-copy">Hi [Customer Name],

Payment received. Thank you.

Your order is now moving to the next step.

Next:
- [Service-only: I will prepare your service access details]
- [Device order: I will prepare your device order and next update]
- [Shipped order: I will follow up with your shipping update once ready]

You can expect the next update [later today / within a few hours / by tomorrow].

Thank you,
Timothy
4MyIPTV Service</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card template-box" id="service-only">
      <h2>Service-Only Fulfillment</h2>
      <div class="template-copy">Hi [Customer Name],

Your service details are ready.

Login details:
- Username: [X]
- Password: [X]
- Server URL: [X]

Next steps:
- Install the recommended player if needed
- Enter the login details exactly as shown
- Use one stream per device unless otherwise discussed

If you need setup help, use this support link:
[Insert support link]

Thank you,
Timothy
4MyIPTV Service</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card template-box" id="device-prep">
      <h2>Device Preparation</h2>
      <div class="template-copy">Hi [Customer Name],

Your order is now being prepared.

Order summary:
- Service term: [X]
- Device: [X]

Next steps:
- Your device will be prepared with the requested setup
- I will follow up with your next update once preparation is complete
- If shipping applies, I will send your shipping update separately

Thank you,
Timothy
4MyIPTV Service</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card template-box" id="shipping-confirmation">
      <h2>Shipping Confirmation</h2>
      <div class="template-copy">Hi [Customer Name],

Your order has shipped.

Shipping details:
- Carrier: [X]
- Tracking number: [X]

Your device has been prepared for your requested setup. If you need help after delivery, use this support link:
[Insert support link]

Thank you,
Timothy
4MyIPTV Service</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card template-box" id="pickup-delivery">
      <h2>Pickup or Delivery Coordination</h2>
      <div class="template-copy">Hi [Customer Name],

Your order is being prepared now.

Once it is ready, I will follow up with your pickup or delivery details.

Order summary:
- Service term: [X]
- Device: [X]

If anything changes before handoff, I will update you directly.

Thank you,
Timothy
4MyIPTV Service</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card template-box" id="support-handoff">
      <h2>Support Handoff</h2>
      <div class="template-copy">Hi [Customer Name],

If you need help with setup or support, use the link below:

[Insert support link]

Please include the same name, email, or phone number used with your order so your request can be matched quickly.

Thank you,
Timothy
4MyIPTV Service</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card template-box" id="renewal-quote">
      <h2>Renewal Quote</h2>
      <div class="template-copy">Hi [Customer Name],

Your service renewal quote is below.

Service term: [Monthly / 6 Months / 1 Year / 2 Years]
Renewal price: [$X]

Total: [$X]

If this looks good, please reply:

Approved

Once approved, I will send your payment instructions.

Thank you,
Timothy
4MyIPTV Service</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card template-box" id="renewal-payment">
      <h2>Renewal Payment</h2>
      <div class="template-copy">Hi [Customer Name],

Thank you. Your renewal is approved and ready for payment.

Renewal summary:
- Service term: [X]
- Total due: [$X]

Payment link:
[Insert payment link]

After payment is completed, I will confirm receipt and follow up with your renewal completion update.

Thank you,
Timothy
4MyIPTV Service</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card template-box" id="renewal-complete">
      <h2>Renewal Complete</h2>
      <div class="template-copy">Hi [Customer Name],

Payment received. Thank you.

Your renewal has been completed.

Updated service term:
- [X]

If you need support, use this link:
[Insert support link]

Thank you,
Timothy
4MyIPTV Service</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Related Internal Pages</h2>
    <div class="section-sub">
      Use these pages alongside the templates to manage the full customer flow.
    </div>
    <div class="action-row">
      <a href="admin-resource-center.html" class="action-btn">Resource Center</a>
      <a href="admin-dashboard.html" class="action-btn">Admin Dashboard</a>
      <a href="admin-orders.html" class="action-btn">Admin Orders</a>
      <a href="admin-customers.html" class="action-btn">Admin Customers</a>
      <a href="admin-checkout-link-generator.html" class="action-btn">Checkout Link Generator</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-strip">
    <strong>4MyIPTV Service • Admin Message Templates</strong>
    <div class="version">Version 1.0 • Last Updated: April 3, 2026</div>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
